{"name":"Spiritual Separation","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You attempt to rip a creature's spirit from its body, supernaturally separating them.</p>\n<p>The target must attempt a Will saving throw.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.<br /><strong>Success</strong> The target becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.dfCMdR4wnpbYNTix]{Stunned 1} as it resists its spirit being tugged away from their body.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target's spirit is removed from its body, causing the target to temporarily become an incorporeal ghost. This ghost shares a pool of Hit Points with its body, which is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.fBnFDH2MTzgFijKf]{Unconscious} until the spirit is reunited with it, and cannot willingly move more than 120 feet away from its body. The target cannot use its equipment, though it may use its unarmed attacks, which become magical and deal negative damage instead of their normal type. If the body is slain, the ghost is destroyed, and vice versa. At the end of each of its turns, the target may attempt another Will save; on a success, they rejoin with their body.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, except the effect is permanent and there is no restriction on how far the ghost may move from its body. If the target was a player character, they become an NPC until this effect is dispelled. At the GM's direction, a player character may instead immediately retrain to gain the @Compendium[pf2e.feats-srd.52nzskpmUt9AjUf8]{Ghost Dedication} feat.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["incapacitation"],"rarity":"rare"},"level":{"value":8},"spellType":{"value":"save"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":["divine","occult"]},"school":{"value":"necromancy"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":"1 living creature"},"range":{"value":"30 feet"},"area":null,"time":{"value":"2"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"will","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686675001493,"modifiedTime":1686676885809,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"2tYSHzEppLZUbeYE","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Painter's Prison","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>This ritual is a variation on the @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.2CNqkt2s2IYkVnv6]{Imprisonment} ritual that allows a skilled painter to trap the target in a painted form within a picture frame.</p>\n<p>The target's form is transferred onto a canvas, rendering it unable to act except to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.1OagaWtBpVXExToo]{Recall Knowledge} and use actions that require only the use of its mind. The creature can still use its senses in this form, and it does not age nor does it require food and drink.</p>\n<p>Destroying the painting kills the target rather than freeing it. This effect can’t be counteracted, though it can be ended by the@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.4ddJSjC9Zz5DX0oG]{Freedom} ritual.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> You imprison the target, and any creatures trying to use a <em>freedom</em> ritual to rescue the target take a –2 circumstance penalty to checks associated with that ritual.<br /><strong>Success</strong> You imprison the target.<br /><strong>Failure</strong> You fail to imprison the target.<br /><strong>Critical Failure</strong> You imprison yourself and the secondary casters within the painting instead of the target.</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Heightened (9th)</strong> You can target a creature of up to 18th level. The base cost increases to 2,000 gp.</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Heightened (10th)</strong> You can target a creature of up to 20th level. The base cost increases to 6,000 gp.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"rare"},"level":{"value":8},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"ritual"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"transmutation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":false},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":"1 creature of up to 16th level"},"range":{"value":"10 feet"},"area":null,"time":{"value":"1 day"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":"magical paints worth a total value of 800 gp × the target’s level"},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"primarycheck":{"value":"Crafting (legendary)"},"secondarycheck":{"value":"Occultism, Society"},"secondarycasters":{"value":"6"}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686676354809,"modifiedTime":1686676885815,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"3NEas2hUkGRWRrfG","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Cucco's Fury","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You call forth an enraged flock of cuccos to harry your enemies and assail them with pecks.</p>\n<p>The flock occupies the space of a Huge creature, can overlap other creatures like a swarm, and has a fly Speed of 60 feet.</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Arrive</strong> <em>Feathered Flurry</em> All spaces occupied by the cuccoo flock are difficult terrain. Additionally, all creatures within the swarm's area are concealed by the mass of cuccos, and all other creatures are concealed to them.</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Depart</strong> <em>Revenge Squad</em> The cucco flock Flies to overlap as many enemies as possible that they witnessed harming you or one of your allies since they arrived, then pecks at them dealing 6d6 piercing damage (basic Reflex save) to all such creatures in the swarm's area.</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 2d6.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["incarnate"],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":3},"spellType":{"value":"save"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":["primal"]},"school":{"value":"conjuration"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":true,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":"100 feet"},"area":null,"time":{"value":"3"},"duration":{"value":"until the end of your next turn"},"damage":{"value":{"DnsjP2r9AKmX1b6R":{"value":"6d6","type":{"value":"piercing","categories":[],"subtype":""},"applyMod":false}}},"save":{"value":"reflex","basic":"basic"},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"heightening":{"type":"interval","interval":1,"damage":{"DnsjP2r9AKmX1b6R":"2d6"}}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686675001493,"modifiedTime":1686676885808,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"3qwtiiH3h6HoZUkd","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Tornado Lift","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You generate a miniature tornado underneath you that lifts you into the air. When you cast this spell, you are lifted 10 feet into the air by a gale. For the duration of the spell, you remain in this elevated position, hovering in place. The tornado that lifts you has the effects of @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.it4ZsAi6XgvGcodc]{Wall of Wind} in all spaces underneath you. The spell ends immediately if you move.</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> You are lifted an additional 5 feet into the air.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["air"],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":2},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":["arcane","primal"]},"school":{"value":"evocation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":false},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":null,"time":{"value":"2"},"duration":{"value":"sustained up to 1 minute"},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686675001493,"modifiedTime":1686676885810,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"7nrnjYR5YWstx4JT","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Unleash Season","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You unleash the full power of the current season.</p>\n<p>This has the effects and traits of another spell, depending on the active seasonal influence when you cast the spell:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.J6vNvrUT3b1hx2iA]{Entangle} for spring,</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.v3vFzGazNSFEDdRB]{Radiant Field} for summer,</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.kvZCQz4NoMAfjvif]{Gasping Marsh} for autumn,</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Popa5umI3H33levx]{Rime Slick} for winter.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>By spending an additional action as you cast this spell, creatures in the area become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.DmAIPqOBomZ7H95W]{Concealed}, as @Compendium[pf2e-adventures-in-hyrule.pf2e-adventures-in-hyrule-spells.oG17SgOZcYF5eWp7]{Seasonal Squall}, in addition to the usual effects.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["cursebound","oracle"],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":6},"spellType":{"value":"attack"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"evocation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":{"value":20,"type":"emanation"},"time":{"value":"2 or 3"},"duration":{"value":"sustained up to 1 minute"},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686073058802,"modifiedTime":1686355048663,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"8jsVbiFvTCFIqF6Y","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Mipha's Grace","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You or a living creature within range would die</p>\n<hr />\n<p><em>You invoke the power of Mipha, appointed champion of the zora, to shield allies from death at the very last moment. </em></p>\n<p>You prevent the target from dying and grant it Hit Points equal to five times its level.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion","healing"],"rarity":"rare"},"level":{"value":7},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"necromancy"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":"the triggering creature"},"range":{"value":"60"},"area":null,"time":{"value":"reaction"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685548674513,"modifiedTime":1685553550999,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"Gj1shRnWUfZ60G0Q","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Wall Merge","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You merge with an adjacent wall large enough to fit a two-dimensional image of you and your possessions. You must touch the wall when you Cast the Spell. While merged with a wall, you appear as a painted facsimile of your form similar to living graffiti. You can hear and see from the wall's surface, and you can Stride or @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.VMozDqMMuK5kpoX4]{Sneak} horizontally along the wall's surface up to your Speed, ignoring gravity as long as you are merged.</p>\n<p>If the surface you are on sustains significant damage, the spell ends and you take [[/r 10d6[bludgeoning]]] damage as you are expelled into the nearest empty space. @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.115Xp9E38CJENhNS]{Passwall} expels you without dealing damage and ends <em>wall merge</em>.</p>\n<p>You can Dismiss this spell.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"rare"},"level":{"value":4},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":["arcane","occult"]},"school":{"value":"transmutation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":null,"time":{"value":"2"},"duration":{"value":"sustained"},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686675001493,"modifiedTime":1686676885812,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"HI9oCoMa4d1IIe2e","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Control Season","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You take control of the very seasons, changing the season within the ritual's area. When you attempt this ritual, you choose a season to change the local area to; if that season is the opposite of the current season, the DC of the primary check is increased by 5.</p>\n<p>You cannot control the specific weather after this ritual takes effect.</p>\n<p>At the end of the ritual's duration, the season gradually returns to its natural state over the course of a month.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The season changes, instantly altering the temperature and weather to match the normal conditions for the new season.<br /><strong>Success</strong> The season changes, with the temperature and weather adjusting over the course of a week to match the normal conditions for the new season.<br /><strong>Failure</strong> You fail to change the season.<br /><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The season changes to the opposite of your chosen season, with the temperature and weather adjusting over the course of a week to match the normal conditions for the new season.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"rare"},"level":{"value":9},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"ritual"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"evocation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":false},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":"5-mile-radius circle centered on you"},"area":null,"time":{"value":"1 week"},"duration":{"value":"3 months"},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"primarycheck":{"value":"Nature (master)"},"secondarycheck":{"value":"Survival"},"secondarycasters":{"value":"2"}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686676354809,"modifiedTime":1686676885813,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"IBDHGiYMrKExQcLn","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Ascend","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You leap upwards towards a ceiling at most 30 feet directly above you, rapidly merging into it and 'swimming' up through at most 30 feet of solid non-magical material. If you reach the upper surface of the material during this movement, you emerge from the floor; otherwise, you are safely returned to the space you Cast this Spell.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The maximum distance you can ascend through material increases by 30 feet.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["move"],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":4},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":["arcane","divine","primal"]},"school":{"value":"transmutation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":null,"time":{"value":"2"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686675001493,"modifiedTime":1686676885807,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"SlHQraHj3kBJ8MrU","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Daruk's Protection","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><em>You invoke the power of Daruk, surrounding yourself in a shimmering red barrier that renders you impervious to harm but limits your abilities. </em></p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.xjGwis0uaC2305pm]{Raise a Shield} or cast <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.TVKNbcgTee19PXZR]{Shield}</em></p>\n<hr />\n<p>The first time you would take damage from a source other than persistent damage or an ongoing affliction, it is absorbed by the shield; this does not protect you from any other negative effects of Strikes that hit you or spells that affect you. The spell ends immediately after absorbing damage this way.</p>\n<p>You can Sustain this Spell as a free action triggered by Raising a Shield or casting <em>shield</em>.</p>\n<p>You cannot cast spells or perform Strikes whilst under the effect of this spell.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.839,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"rare"},"level":{"value":7},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"abjuration"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":null,"time":{"value":"free"},"duration":{"value":"Sustained"},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685222948137,"modifiedTime":1685327981870,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"UgauRj7dQfQ2h5i0","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Urbosa's Fury","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><em>You invoke the power of Urbosa, unleashing a storm of lightning as you make a wild attack. </em></p>\n<p>Make a Strike against each adjacent creature, using the same unarmed attack or weapon for all of these Strikes; these strikes contribute to and use your multiple attack penalty. The storm then deals 15d10 electricity damage to creatures in the area. Each creature in the area must attempt a Reflex save.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.<br /><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.<br /><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage.<br /><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.dfCMdR4wnpbYNTix]{Stunned 1}.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.839,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion","electricity"],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":7},"spellType":{"value":"save"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":["divine"]},"school":{"value":"evocation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":{"value":10,"type":"emanation"},"time":{"value":"2 rounds"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{"h3oBRXzTxgiadAql":{"value":"15d10","type":{"value":"electricity","categories":[],"subtype":""},"applyMod":false}}},"save":{"value":"reflex","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685159944681,"modifiedTime":1685492024151,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"WH8lx5TBWN7ffozN","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Invigorating Kiss","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>A magical kiss grants your ally a little extra strength to carry on.</p>\n<p>You grant your ally temporary Hit Points equal to double your level that last as long as you @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.3f5DMFu8fPiqHpRg]{Sustain} the spell. Once this spell ends, the target becomes temporarily immune for 1 minute.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf2e-adventures-in-hyrule.pf2e-adventures-in-hyrule-effects.srzqs59cVSANgURj]{Spell Effect: Invigorating Kiss}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["cantrip","enchantment","hex","mental","witch"],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":1},"spellType":{"value":"heal"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"enchantment"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":false},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":"1 willing creature"},"range":{"value":"touch"},"area":null,"time":{"value":"1"},"duration":{"value":"sustained up to 1 minute"},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZkaxNKYoTzpZNs9a"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686074531283,"modifiedTime":1686447002193,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"ZkaxNKYoTzpZNs9a","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Kooloo-Limpah!","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><em>With a special song and dance, you throw magical confetti which manifests magic in an unpredictable way. </em></p>\n<p>Roll [[/r 1d8]] on the following table to determine this spell's effects. This spell gains any traits for the chosen effect(s).</p>\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width:5.57554%\">d8</th>\n<th style=\"width:94.4245%\">Effect</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.57554%\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width:94.4245%\"><strong>Regular Confetti</strong> Nothing happens, and if this was the only effect, you regain the focus point spent to cast this spell.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.57554%\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width:94.4245%\">\n<p><strong>Defective Bomb</strong> A lit bomb materialises next to an ally, dealing [[/r (2 * @item.level)d6[fire]]]{2d6 fire damage per spell level} (basic Reflex save) in a @Template[type:burst|distance:15] centered on a random ally within 30 feet.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.57554%\">3</td>\n<td style=\"width:94.4245%\">\n<p><strong>Tingle Bomb</strong> A lit bomb materialises in a space of your choice within 60 feet, dealing [[/r (2 * @item.level)d6[fire]]]{2d6 fire damage per spell level} (basic Reflex save) in a @Template[type:burst|distance:15].</p>\n<p><em>Inline Reflex save: @Check[type:reflex|dc:resolve(@spell.spellcasting.statistic.abilityModifier.modifier)]</em></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.57554%\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width:94.4245%\"><strong>Healing Ting</strong> (healing) You restore [[/r (2 * @item.level)d8[healing]]]{2d8 Hit Points per spell level} to an ally of your choice within 30 feet.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.57554%\">5</td>\n<td style=\"width:94.4245%\"><strong>Tingle Fortune</strong> (prediction) Choose one ally within 30 feet; they may ask about an action they intend to take during their next turn. The GM tells them whether taking that course of action is a good idea, a bad idea, or neither.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.57554%\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width:94.4245%\">\n<p><strong>Tingle Shield</strong> A magical shield appears around an ally of your choice within 30 feet, granting resistance to all damage equal to double this spell's level until the end of their next turn.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf2e-adventures-in-hyrule.pf2e-adventures-in-hyrule-effects.giA8rIpSyyLPm2w8]{Effect: Kooloo-Limpah! (Tingle Shield)}</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.57554%\">7</td>\n<td style=\"width:94.4245%\"><strong>Tingle Balloon</strong> (air) An ally of your choice within 30 feet becomes as light as a balloon, able to float through the air momentarily. This has the effects of @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.b5sGjGlBf58f8jn0]{Air Walk}, with a duration of a number of rounds equal to twice this spell's level.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.57554%\">8</td>\n<td style=\"width:94.4245%\"><strong>Supercharge</strong> Roll twice more, rerolling any results of 8.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":3},"spellType":{"value":"attack"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"conjuration"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":true,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":null,"time":{"value":"2"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686018909449,"modifiedTime":1686668338975,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"ccovuHNNRfFTb3Oz","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Diurnal Inversion","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You invert the apparent cycle of day and night within the spell's area. The level of light, as well as the behavior of animals, adjusts over the course of a minute when the ritual is complete.</p>\n<p>Viewed from outside, the affected area appears to be in a constant state of twilight.</p>\n<p>Casting this ritual again restores the natural cycle of day and night.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> You invert the cycle of day and night in a larger area (up to a 5-mile-radius circle), or for twice as long as normal.<br /><strong>Success</strong> You invert the cycle of day and night.<br /><strong>Failure</strong> You fail to invert the cycle of day and night.<br /><strong>Critical Failure</strong> You fail to invert the cycle of day and night, but experience the passing of several days in a single moment, becoming @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.HL2l2VRSaQHu9lUw]{Fatigued} for 24 hours.</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Heightened (9th)</strong> The ritual's duration increases to 1 month.</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Heightened (10th)</strong> The ritual's duration increases to 3 months.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["darkness","light"],"rarity":"rare"},"level":{"value":8},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"ritual"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"illusion"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":false},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":"2-mile-radius circle centered on you"},"area":null,"time":{"value":"1 day"},"duration":{"value":"1 week"},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"primarycheck":{"value":"Nature (master)"},"secondarycheck":{"value":"Survival"},"secondarycasters":{"value":"1"}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686676354809,"modifiedTime":1686676885814,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"dDURdcwrs4dDgPIe","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Timeshift","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You create a field that reverts an area to appear as it was in the previous era. All artificial structures, objects and hazards created in the current era vanish for the spell's duration, and ruins from the previous era are restored to an intact state.</p>\n<p>Any creature that would be placed inside an object as a result of this spell is harmlessly ejected to the nearest empty space.</p>\n<p>Further effects may occur at the GM's discretion, such as terrain within the spell's area changing its nature; for example, if the spell is used in an desert that used to be grassland, difficult terrain in the spell's area may become regular terrain instead as the sand dunes are replaced by gentle hills.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"rare"},"level":{"value":5},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":["arcane","occult"]},"school":{"value":"transmutation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":"30 feet"},"area":{"value":20,"type":"burst"},"time":{"value":"2"},"duration":{"value":"sustained up to 1 minute"},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686675001493,"modifiedTime":1686676885810,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"dEr7MqLMKVyZqfwS","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Season's Protection","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Trigger</strong> You are about to attempt a save against an effect with a trait associated with a season.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Choose any season which shares an associated trait with a trait of the triggering effect. Your active seasonal influence immediately changes to that season, and does not change at the start of your next turn. Then, you roll the triggering save twice and use the better result.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["cursebound","fortune","oracle"],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":3},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"abjuration"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":false},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":null,"time":{"value":"reaction"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686073058802,"modifiedTime":1686075034603,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"eaZRIYByxWkbqNQS","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Revali's Gale","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Area</strong> 15-foot radius, 60-foot tall cylinder centered on you</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You invoke the power of Revali, appointed champion of the rito, creating a massive upwards gust. You immediately create a powerful cylindrical updraft, 15 feet wide and 60 feet tall centered on your space, with the following effects.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ammunition from physical ranged attacks—such as arrows, bolts, sling bullets, and other objects of similar size—can't pass through the gale. Attacks with bigger ranged weapons, such as javelins, take a –2 circumstance penalty to their attack rolls if their paths pass through the gale. Massive ranged weapons and spell effects that don't create physical objects pass through the wall with no penalty.</li>\n<li>The gale is greater difficult terrain to creatures attempting to descend through it. Gases, including creatures in gaseous form, can't pass through the gale.</li>\n<li>Flying upwards through the gale isn't difficult terrain.</li>\n<li>Creatures inside the gale can @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.d5I6018Mci2SWokk]{Leap} to ride the gale upwards. This propels them to the top of the gale, though they fall with the effects of @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.TTwOKGqmZeKSyNMH]{Feather Fall} immediately after using their next action.</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["air","champion"],"rarity":"rare"},"level":{"value":7},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"evocation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":{"value":15,"type":"burst"},"time":{"value":"3"},"duration":{"value":"until the end of your next turn"},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685491260751,"modifiedTime":1685553551000,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"kVK6UD02vYawgLlX","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Seasonal Squall","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You invoke the season's harshest weather, becoming the eye of a storm which varies based on your seasonal influence.</p>\n<p>The squall deals 2d6 damage of a type based on the active season, subject to a basic Reflex save. In addition, until the start of your next turn, all creatures within the area are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.DmAIPqOBomZ7H95W]{Concealed}, and all other creatures are concealed to them. This spell gains any traits listed in brackets for the current effects.</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Spring</strong> (water) heavy rain deals bludgeoning damage, which also conceals creatures.</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Summer</strong> (fire) scouring heat deals fire damage, and a heat haze conceals creatures.</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Autumn</strong> (negative) fell winds deal negative damage, and dark fog conceals creatures.</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Winter</strong> (cold) frosty gales deal cold damage, and snow conceals creatures.</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 2d6.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["cursebound","oracle"],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":1},"spellType":{"value":"save"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"evocation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":{"value":5,"type":"emanation"},"time":{"value":"2"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"reflex","basic":"basic"},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"overlays":{"9eiEtPdIQmk7mH89":{"name":"Seasonal Squall (Summer)","system":{"traits":{"value":["cursebound","fire","oracle"]},"damage":{"value":{"nY6ckHJ8dfNKSztH":{"value":"2d6","type":{"value":"fire","categories":[],"subtype":""},"applyMod":false}}},"heightening":{"type":"interval","interval":1,"damage":{"nY6ckHJ8dfNKSztH":"2d6"}}},"sort":2,"_stats":{"modifiedTime":1686073363399},"_id":"9eiEtPdIQmk7mH89","overlayType":"override"},"luH0lhvS1F3BkJip":{"name":"Seasonal Squall (Spring)","system":{"traits":{"value":["cursebound","oracle","water"]},"damage":{"value":{"fZGVK6RO4QdDHy2b":{"value":"2d6","type":{"value":"bludgeoning","categories":[],"subtype":""},"applyMod":false}}},"heightening":{"type":"interval","interval":1,"damage":{"fZGVK6RO4QdDHy2b":"2d6"}}},"sort":1,"_stats":{"modifiedTime":1686073310362},"_id":"luH0lhvS1F3BkJip","overlayType":"override"},"R9EDyJgzWrkqAmPq":{"name":"Seasonal Squall (Autumn)","system":{"damage":{"value":{"WrbAdxajyN7fw8qJ":{"value":"2d6","type":{"value":"negative","categories":[],"subtype":""},"applyMod":false}}},"heightening":{"type":"interval","interval":1,"damage":{"WrbAdxajyN7fw8qJ":"2d6"}}},"sort":3,"_stats":{"modifiedTime":1686073422784},"_id":"R9EDyJgzWrkqAmPq","overlayType":"override"},"AmXmqUguTuW1fKNM":{"name":"Seasonal Squall (Winter)","system":{"damage":{"value":{"LeIDrkVLZko1ZeA7":{"value":"2d6","type":{"value":"cold","categories":[],"subtype":""},"applyMod":false}}},"heightening":{"type":"interval","interval":1,"damage":{"LeIDrkVLZko1ZeA7":"2d6"}}},"sort":4,"_stats":{"modifiedTime":1686073459036},"_id":"AmXmqUguTuW1fKNM","overlayType":"override"}}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686073058802,"modifiedTime":1686075034602,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"oG17SgOZcYF5eWp7","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Dead Man's Volley","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You generate a slow-moving orb of force, launching it at a foe.</p>\n<p>Make a spell attack roll. The target of this spell may use their reaction to attempt to reflect the orb at a new target within 30 feet by making a melee Strike against the caster's spell DC; the result of the Strike determines the degree of success of this spell against the new target if they do not successfully reflect it in turn. If an attempt at reflecting the orb would result in a miss, the orb is not reflected and the attempting creature takes damage based on the result of the previous attack roll.</p>\n<p>On a hit, the spell deals 6d8 force damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target takes double damage unless they successfully use a reaction to reflect the orb, and the next attempt to reflect the orb uses a degree of success one step worse than was rolled.<br /><strong>Success</strong> The target takes normal damage unless they successfully use a reaction to reflect the orb.</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 2d8.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["force"],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":3},"spellType":{"value":"attack"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":["arcane","occult"]},"school":{"value":"evocation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":"1 creature"},"range":{"value":"30 feet"},"area":null,"time":{"value":"2"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{"oiNO1UhIGFSEIXmA":{"value":"6d8","type":{"value":"force","categories":[],"subtype":""},"applyMod":false}}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"heightening":{"type":"interval","interval":1,"damage":{"oiNO1UhIGFSEIXmA":"2d8"}}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686675001493,"modifiedTime":1686676885808,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"p06BEbXH2dKr0VMg","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Bubble Blast","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><em>You inflate a large bubble and then send it flying towards a foe. </em></p>\n<p>Make a spell attack. If you hit, you deal 1d6 bludgeoning damage plus 1 bludgeoning splash damage. If you spent 3 actions Casting this Spell, the range increases to 60 feet and the splash damage radius increases by 5 feet (for a total of 10 feet).</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Heightened (+2)</strong> The damage increases by 1d6 and the splash radius when you use 3 actions to Cast the Spell increases by 5 feet</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.839,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["air","attack","cantrip","evocation"],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":1},"spellType":{"value":"attack"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":["arcane","primal"]},"school":{"value":"evocation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":"1 creature"},"range":{"value":"30 feet"},"area":null,"time":{"value":"2 to 3"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{"f1pqY81ggl56nENJ":{"value":"1d6","type":{"value":"bludgeoning","categories":[],"subtype":""},"applyMod":false},"wqkGZSJpCs1C33cp":{"value":"1","type":{"value":"bludgeoning","categories":[],"subtype":"splash"},"applyMod":false}}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"heightening":{"type":"interval","interval":2,"damage":{"f1pqY81ggl56nENJ":"0","wqkGZSJpCs1C33cp":"0"}}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1684810113443,"modifiedTime":1686675412423,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"xw4YQonnwYrIcyjb","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
{"name":"Command Melody","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You perform a mystical melody that allows you to command others, including normally inanimate statues.</p>\n<p>You project your senses into the target, and they become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.9qGBRpbX9NEwtAAr]{Controlled} by you.</p>\n<p>If you targeted a statue of size Large or smaller, the statue additionally becomes animate for the duration of the spell, using the statistics of an @Compendium[pf2e.pathfinder-bestiary.PiAGhPEzJMC2egQk]{Animated Statue}.</p>\n<p>You lose access to your senses for the duration of the spell.</p>\n<p>Both you and the target can Dismiss the spell to end its effects early.</p>\n<p>After casting this spell on a willing creature, you become linked until your next daily preparations, allowing you to target them with further castings of <em>command melody</em> regardless of distance as long as you both remain within 1 mile of the original casting site.</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Heightened (6th)</strong> You can target a Huge statue, using the statistics for a @Compendium[pf2e.pathfinder-bestiary.wKVZdVVcXtvLxgsY]{Giant Animated Statue}.</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Heightened (10th)</strong> You can target a Gargantuan statue, using the statistics for an @Compendium[pf2e.pathfinder-bestiary-3.4WMThCqvHV1aaBwa]{Animated Colossus}.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Adventures in Hyrule"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["bard","possession"],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":4},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"enchantment"},"components":{"focus":true,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":"1 inanimate statue or willing creature"},"range":{"value":"30 feet"},"area":null,"time":{"value":"3"},"duration":{"value":"10 minutes"},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686675001493,"modifiedTime":1686676885812,"lastModifiedBy":"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq"},"_id":"yCu1qCl7if56RMBf","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"rfqfWP0e50JaIRVq":3}}
